<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/677837-can-this-be-read-as-a-stand-alone">Can this be read as a stand-alone?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_677837'><a id="like_count_community_question_677837" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/677837?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">7 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F11734.The_Human_Stain">like</a></span>

